%Variables%
%variable%
%variables_dialog%
%Variables Dialog%
Most configuration settings of Z-Mail are stored in variables.  To see
or change the settings of the variables, you use the Variables
dialog. Select the Variables item from the Options menu of the
~#Main Window#~ to bring up the Variables dialog.

The scrolled list at the left of the dialog lists all the Z-Mail
variables.  The Variable Description: field contains information
about the variable currently selected in the scrolled list. To
change the setting of a particular variable, select its name
