%dates_dialog%
The Date Search dialog lets you search for
messages in the active folder, or all the open
folders, that were sent in a date range you
specify.  Choose the Date Search... item from the
Find menu of the ~#Main Window#~ to bring up the
Date Search dialog.

To specify a date, move the slider above the
calendar to the year, select the month from the
list to the right of the calendar, and click on
the desired day. Choose one of the four radio
buttons no the lower right of the dialog to
specify how to search relative to the date you
