%Composing Messages%

You can compose and send new messages, edit and
forward existing messages, and compose a reply
to existing messages, using the Compose
Window. 

To send a new message, open a Compose Window
from the Main Window or while reading
messages in the Message Display Window.

To compose a new message,

  - Choose "Compose New" from the Compose
    menu, or click on the Compose button in 
    the Main Window.

For information about replying to and
forwarding messages, see ~#Replying to a Message#~
and ~#Forwarding Messages#~.

