%Address Editing%
To edit addresses in the Address List:
  
  1. Select the address or addresses you want to edit 
     by clicking on them in the Address List.
  
  2. Click on one of the buttons to the left of the 
  
     Address List. Select from:
  
     Edit      Copy the selected address or addresses 
               to the Address Entry Area.
  
     Expand    Expand an alias into its real address or
               addresses, separate multiple-address 
               aliases, and copy the expanded address 
               or addresses to the Address Entry Area.
  
