%Searching%
To search for a pattern in the text of a message
you're reading, use the "Search Text" dialog.
You can bring up the Search Text dialog with the
Search... item of the Find menu in the
~#Message Display Window#~.

To find and optionally replace patterns in
a message you're composing, bring up 
the ~#Search and Replace#~ dialog by
choosing  the "Search/Replace/Spell..."
item on the Edit menu in the ~#Compose Window#~.

To search for messages containing a particular
string, use the ~#Pattern Search dialog#~.

To search for messages received during a specific
time period, use the ~#Date Search dialog#~.
